    "DiscussionOur results demonstrate that introspective behavior-detecting and identifying transient activation injectionscan be reliably trained in small models.",
    "We first situate our findings within Lindsey's framework, then discuss implications.",
    "Evaluating Against Lindsey's CriteriaLindsey [2025] proposes four criteria for introspective awareness: accuracy, grounding, internality, and metacognitive representation.",
    "He tests these across four experiments; we focus on the first (injected-thought detection) and evaluate how our trained model performs on each criterion for this task:Criterion 1: Accuracy.",
    "Lindsey's best model (Claude Opus 4.1) achieves ∼20% success on concept identification."
  ],
